{"tid":2105270,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"十大屋苑周末成交增四成 代理料樓市穩定","createTime":"2020-07-12T13:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T14:27:06.000Z","uid":166360,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"db76441864d6685595217f1822d7b1e4668b2b99","tid":2105270,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"十大屋苑周末成交增四成 代理料樓市穩定<br />\n文章日期：2020年7月12日 19:32<br />\n<br />\n&quot;雖然新冠肺炎疫情再轉壞，加上周末有大型新盤推售，不過，二手屋苑成交卻有所增加。中原地產統計，十大屋苑本周末錄得14宗成交，較上周末增加4宗或40%，已連續7個周末保持雙位數成交，其中最多成交為天水圍嘉湖山莊共錄4宗，另鰂魚涌太古城則錄得3宗成交...&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1594553974241&amp;issue=20200712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1594553974241%26issue%3D20200712&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=fd97fc92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1594553974241&amp;issue=20200712</a>"},{"pid":"a627b79e048443ea2e98edcb63c1545b839e64f7","tid":2105270,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T13:51:19.000Z","msg":"樓市gogogo"},{"pid":"98f755b71cf3db8340fc61e438bf96dc452ed889","tid":2105270,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:16:03.000Z","msg":"接火棒"},{"pid":"762a823c21a34d7d0041c297def6aab8e26ea0f2","tid":2105270,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"豪賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a79e761afbd431a32c110cb9a13b191dc82d99","tid":2105270,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"762a823c21a34d7d0041c297def6aab8e26ea0f2","tid":2105270,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:22:37.000Z","msg":